Package com.luke.lukef.lukeapp.fragments

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AchievementFragment
    Fragment displayed in one of the tabs in the ProfileFragment.
    LeaderboardFragment
    Fragment that displays a listview of top users.
    MapViewFragment
    Handles the Map view, fetches submissions, populates map with Submissions and Admin markers.
    NewSubmissionFragment
    Handles the new submission screen, includes sending the submissions, dispatching the camera intent and listening to the category pop up clicks.
    ProfileFragment
    Handles the profile fragment, setting up the tab layout for achievements and submissions
    UserSubmissionFragment
    Fragment to be passed into the tablayout that displays all of a users submissions in a cardview
